messages.messageBody:
there is raising witches, a yahoo group. here's their description:
Description

**** The Messages are no longer archived,you can still recieve
messages thru your email! Remember, keep on Individual Emails or
Daily Digest! (Special notice & No Mail are not accepted.****

This is a group geared toward the raising of Pagan children in
today's closed-minded world. This is an International group, so
anyone, not only people in the US, but other countries may joine. All
that is required is that you have children or are a Grandparent,
Aunt, Stepmother, Mother-in-law, etc. Even Fathers, Grandfathers,
Uncles, Stepfathers, & Father-in-laws are welcome to joine. We have a
2 more groups, called Raising_Witches_2,and Raising_Witches_3,
Raising_Witches_4, & Raising_Witches_5. They are only for storage,
that's pretty much it. You may join that group from the link below
after joining this group first.
Let's celebrate our Pagan/Wiccan/Witchy/eclectic/etc. Roots and raise
our kids the way we want to!!!

~~~Teens may joine:
http://groups.yahoo.com/group_Raising_Witches_Teens/ There is a
disclaimer that is sent out upon joining if you wish to do so. Please
keep a copy of it if you do.~~~

Your group owner,
Elisa Aurora "Salice Della Luna"
